# Project Conventions

This project is a generic FastAPI + SvelteKit monorepo boilerplate.

## Routing

API routes live in:

apps/example-api/app/api/routes

Routes must:
- remain thin
- validate input
- call service functions

Routes must NOT contain business logic.

## Services

Business logic lives in:

apps/example-api/app/services

Services should:
- contain application logic
- be deterministic unless explicitly integrating an external provider
- return structured data objects

## Schemas

Pydantic schemas live in:

apps/example-api/app/schemas

All API inputs and outputs must use schemas.

## Testing

Tests live in:

apps/example-api/tests

Each endpoint should have:
- success test
- validation or method/error test where applicable

## Dependencies

Do not introduce heavy frameworks unless required.

Specifically avoid adding:
- LangChain
- Celery
- database ORMs

until the architecture requires them.
